        argument: `早期吠陀文献中的「凯拉萨」是一个神话化的概念，象征着喜马拉雅山脉的神圣性，后来才被具体化为冈仁波齐这座特定的山峰。`,
        argumentEn: `Early Vedic "Kailasa" was a mythologized concept symbolizing the Himalayas' sacredness, later localized to the specific peak of Mount Kailash.`
      }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title="冈仁波齐文化 - 冈仁波齐的千年信仰传承 | Sacred Mountain Culture" description="探索冈仁波齐的千年信仰传承：藏传佛教、印度教、苯教、耆那教四大宗教的神圣交汇。深度文化解读、历史传说与地理奇观。Explore the millennia of faith traditions at Mount Kailash.">

  <!-- Hero: Photo on top, content below -->
  <section class="relative bg-kailash-dark">
    <!-- Full-width photo - moderate height -->
    <div class="relative w-full h-[45vh] lg:h-[55vh]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('/images/kailash-lake.webp')] bg-cover bg-top"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-kailash-dark/30 to-kailash-dark"></div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Content below photo -->
    <div class="relative -mt-12 z-10 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-kailash-gold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Sacred Mountain Culture · 冈仁波齐文化</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">
          冈仁波齐
          <span class="block text-kailash-gold mt-1">千年信仰传承</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/60 mb-1 font-light">
          四大宗教共同的圣地，亚洲文明的 spiritual 中心
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-white/40 italic">
          Four Religions, One Mountain · 不同信仰，同一座山
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- Table of Contents -->
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <TableOfContents items={tocItems} />
  </div>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-light">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-gray-700">
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6 text-center font-light">
          在西藏阿里地区，海拔6656米的冈仁波齐峰静静矗立。它不只是一座山，而是四个古老宗教的共同信仰中心，是亚洲数十亿人心中的精神坐标。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 text-center text-gray-500 italic">
          At 6,656 meters in Tibet's Ngari Prefecture, Mount Kailash stands in stillness. It is not merely a mountain, but a shared center of faith for four ancient religions, a spiritual coordinate in the hearts of billions across Asia.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-md my-8">
          <p class="mb-4">
            藏传佛教称它为<strong>「岗仁波切」</strong>（Gang Rinpoche），意为珍贵的雪山，是胜乐金刚的居所；
            印度教称它为<strong>「凯拉萨」</strong>（Kailasa），是湿婆神的冥想宝座；
            苯教称它为<strong>宇宙之轴</strong>，是天地人三界的连接点；
            耆那教称它为<strong>「八足山」</strong>（Astapada），是第一位祖师获得解脱的地方。
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-500 italic text-sm">
            Tibetan Buddhism calls it <strong>「Gang Rinpoche」</strong> (Precious Snow Mountain), home of Chakrasamvara.
            Hinduism calls it <strong>「Kailasa,」</strong> Shiva's meditation throne.
            Bön calls it the <strong>Cosmic Axis,</strong> connecting heaven, earth, and humanity.
            Jainism calls it <strong>「Astapada,」</strong> where the first Tirthankara attained liberation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center text-lg">
          这座山的独特之处在于：它不是某一宗教的专属财产，而是所有信仰者平等朝拜的圣地。
        </p>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-500 italic text-sm">
          This mountain's uniqueness: it is no single religion's exclusive property, but a sacred site where all believers worship as equals.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Timeline -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">历史时间线</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 italic">Timeline of Sacred History</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="zh">从史前时期到现代朝圣，跨越三千年的信仰传承</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">From prehistoric times to modern pilgrimage, a 3000-year legacy of faith</p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-kailash-gold/30 transform md:-translate-x-1/2"></div>
        {timeline.map((item, index) => (
          <div class={`relative flex items-start mb-12 last:mb-0 ${index % 2 === 0 ? 'md:flex-row' : 'md:flex-row-reverse'}`}>
            <div class="absolute left-4 md:left-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-lg transform md:-translate-x-1/2 mt-1.5 z-10"></div>
            <div class={`ml-12 md:ml-0 md:w-5/12 ${index % 2 === 0 ? 'md:pr-12 md:text-right' : 'md:pl-12'}`}>
              <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <span class="text-kailash-gold font-bold text-sm tracking-wider">{item.year}</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs block">{item.yearEn}</span>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mt-1 mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 italic mb-3">{item.titleEn}</p>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-2">{item.content}</p>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs italic">{item.contentEn}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:block md:w-5/12"></div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Four Religions -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-dark text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-2">四大宗教的冈仁波齐观</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 italic">How Four Religions See the Sacred Mountain</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="zh">每个宗教都有自己独特的冈仁波齐叙事和历史传承</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Each religion has its own unique Kailash narrative and historical legacy</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {religions.map((religion, index) => (
          <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 hover:border-kailash-gold/30 transition-colors">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
              <div class="text-4xl">{religion.icon}</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold">{religion.name}</h3>
                <p class="text-kailash-gold text-sm italic">{religion.nameEn}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">{religion.description}</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm italic leading-relaxed border-t border-white/10 pt-4">{religion.descriptionEn}</p>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 border-l-4 border-kailash-gold mt-4">
              <h4 class="text-kailash-gold text-sm font-semibold mb-2">历史溯源 / Historical Origins</h4>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">{religion.history}</div>
              <div class="text-gray-500 text-xs italic mt-2 whitespace-pre-line">{religion.historyEn}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Historical Figures -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-light">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">历史人物</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 italic">Key Historical Figures</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="zh">塑造冈仁波齐宗教地位的关键人物</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Key figures who shaped Kailash's religious significance</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        {
          [
            { key: '藏传佛教', icon: '📿', color: 'bg-red-50 border-red-200', textColor: 'text-red-800' },
            { key: '印度教', icon: '🕉️', color: 'bg-orange-50 border-orange-200', textColor: 'text-orange-800' },
            { key: '苯教', icon: '☸️', color: 'bg-blue-50 border-blue-200', textColor: 'text-blue-800' },
            { key: '耆那教', icon: '🪔', color: 'bg-green-50 border-green-200', textColor: 'text-green-800' },
            { key: '探险家与学者', icon: '📚', color: 'bg-gray-50 border-gray-200', textColor: 'text-gray-800' }
          ].map((cat) => {
            const figures = historicalFigures.filter(f => f.category === cat.key);
            if (figures.length === 0) return null;
            
            return (
              <div class={`rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 ${cat.color} border-2`}>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 pb-4 border-b-2 border-current border-opacity-20">
                  <span class="text-3xl">{cat.icon}</span>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class={`font-display text-2xl font-bold ${cat.textColor}`}>{cat.key}</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">{figures[0].categoryEn}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                  {figures.map((figure) => (
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-kailash-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl shrink-0">
                          {figure.religionIcon}
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                          <h4 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark">{figure.name}</h4>
                          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mb-2">{figure.nameEn}</p>
                          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                            <span class="text-xs bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-2 py-1 rounded font-medium">{figure.period}</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">{figure.religion}</span>
                          </div>
                          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">{figure.description}</p>
                          <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs italic mt-2 leading-relaxed">{figure.descriptionEn}</p>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            );
          })
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Academic Debates -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">学术争议</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 italic">Academic Debates</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="zh">关于冈仁波齐历史和宗教地位的未解之谜</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Unsolved mysteries about Kailash's history and religious status</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        {academicDebates.map((debate, index) => (
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">{debate.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mb-6">{debate.titleEn}</p>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              {debate.positions.map((position, pIdx) => (
                <div class={`rounded-xl p-6 ${pIdx === 0 ? 'bg-white border-l-4 border-kailash-gold' : 'bg-white border-l-4 border-gray-300'}`}>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark mb-2">{position.side}</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 italic mb-3">{position.sideEn}</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">{position.argument}</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs italic mt-2">{position.argumentEn}</p>
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Legends -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-light">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">传说与神话</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 italic">Sacred Legends & Mythology</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="zh">流传千年的冈仁波齐故事，信仰与历史的交织</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Millennia-old Kailash stories, the interweaving of faith and history</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        {legends.map((legend, index) => (
          <details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer p-8">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-kailash-dark font-bold text-xl">
                  {index + 1}
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark">{legend.title}</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">{legend.titleEn}</p>
                  <p class="text-kailash-gold text-sm font-medium mt-1">{legend.summary}</p>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs italic">{legend.summaryEn}</p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-kailash-gold group-open:hidden">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="text-kailash-gold hidden group-open:block">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 15l7-7 7 7"/></svg>
                </div>
              </div>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-8 pt-0">
              <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6 ml-16">
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4 whitespace-pre-line">{legend.content}</p>
                <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-lg p-4">
                  <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line">{legend.contentEn}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Meaning of Kora -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">转山的四重意义</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 italic">The Four Dimensions of Kora</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {koraMeaning.map((item, index) => (
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-kailash-dark font-bold text-2xl">{index + 1}</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic mb-3">{item.titleEn}</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3">{item.content}</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs italic">{item.contentEn}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Geographical Features -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-dark text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold mb-2">地理奇观</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 italic">Geographical Wonders</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {geoFeatures.map((feature, index) => (
          <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold mb-1">{feature.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 italic mb-4">{feature.titleEn}</p>
            <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">{feature.content}</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic mt-4">{feature.contentEn}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Horse Year Pilgrimage Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f6f3 0%, #ede6d8 50%, #f8f6f3 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-1 mb-4">
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-blue-500"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-300"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 ml-2" data-lang-content="zh">经幡五色 · 蓝天白云红火绿水黄土</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-400 ml-2" data-lang-content="en" style="display:none">Prayer Flag Colors · Sky Cloud Fire Water Earth</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-red-700 text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2 font-medium" data-lang-content="zh">藏历火马年</p>
        <p class="text-red-700 text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-2 font-medium" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Tibetan Fire Horse Year</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="zh">马年转山：历史与信仰</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-3" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Horse Year Pilgrimage</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">客观记录 · 藏传佛教专属朝圣体系</p>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Documented · Exclusive to Tibetan Buddhism</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {horseYearFacts.map((fact, i) => (
          <div class={`bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 overflow-hidden ${i === 0 ? 'md:col-span-2' : ''}`}>
            <div class="flex flex-col h-full">
              {/* 顶部色条 */}
              <div class="h-1 flex">
                {[0,1,2,3,4].map(j => (
                  <div class="flex-1" style={`background:${['#2563eb','#ffffff','#dc2626','#16a34a','#ca8a04'][j]};${j===1?'border-b border-gray-200':''}`}></div>
                ))}
              </div>
              <div class="p-6 md:p-8 flex-1">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-kailash-dark text-white">0{i + 1}</span>
                  <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-display font-bold text-kailash-dark">
                    <span data-lang-content="zh">{fact.label}</span>
                    <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">{fact.labelEn}</span>
                  </h3>
                  <span class={`text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full ${fact.religionColor || 'bg-gray-100 text-gray-600'}`}>
                    <span data-lang-content="zh">{fact.religion}</span>
                    <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">{fact.religionEn}</span>
                  </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base">
                  <span data-lang-content="zh">{fact.content}</span>
                  <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">{fact.contentEn}</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-10 text-gray-400 text-sm">
        <p data-lang-content="zh">下一次马年：2038年（土马年）</p>
        <p data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Next Horse Year: 2038 (Earth Horse)</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Classic Literature Quotes Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-light">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">经典文献深度解读</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 italic">In-Depth Classic Texts Analysis</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="zh">跨越千年的经典著作对冈仁波齐的详细阐释与解读</p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mt-2" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Detailed interpretations of millennia-old classic texts on Kailash</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        {bookQuotes.map((quote, index) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <!-- Book Header -->
            <div class="bg-kailash-dark text-white p-6 md:p-8">
              <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                  <span class="text-4xl">📖</span>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold">{quote.book}</h3>
                    <p class="text-kailash-gold text-lg italic">{quote.bookEn}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-right">
                  <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">{quote.author && `作者：${quote.author}`}</p>
                  <p class="text-kailash-gold text-sm font-medium">{quote.chapter}</p>
                  <p class="text-white/60 text-xs italic">{quote.chapterEn}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Quote Content -->
            <div class="p-6 md:p-8">
              <div class="mb-8">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-kailash-dark font-bold">引</span>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark">经典原文</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-kailash-gold p-6 rounded-r-xl">
                  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                    {quote.fullQuote.split('\n\n').map((paragraph, pIdx) => (
                      <p class="text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mb-4 last:mb-0">{paragraph}</p>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- English Translation -->
              <div class="mb-8">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-gray-600 font-bold">译</span>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-600">English Translation</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-gray-300 p-6 rounded-r-xl">
                  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
                    {quote.fullQuoteEn.split('\n\n').map((paragraph, pIdx) => (
                      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4 last:mb-0 italic">{paragraph}</p>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Interpretation -->
              <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-xl p-6">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                  <span class="w-8 h-8 bg-kailash-dark rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">解</span>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-kailash-dark">深度解读</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="prose max-w-none">
                  {quote.interpretation.split('\n\n').map((paragraph, pIdx) => (
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-3 last:mb-0">{paragraph}</p>
                  ))}
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-kailash-gold/20">
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">{quote.interpretationEn}</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Affiliate Link (only for real books, not Ramayana/Skanda Purana) -->
              {!quote.book.includes('罗摩衍那') && !quote.book.includes('室犍陀往世书') && (
                <div class="mt-6 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
                  <a
                    href={`https://www.amazon.com/s?k=${encodeURIComponent(quote.bookEn || quote.book)}`}
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener nofollow"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-kailash-gold hover:text-kailash-accent transition group"
                  >
                    <span class="opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition">📚</span>
                    <span data-lang-content="zh">在Amazon搜索此书</span>
                    <span data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Search on Amazon</span>
                    <span class="text-xs opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition -ml-1">→</span>
                  </a>
                </div>
              )}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Seasons -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-light">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-2">四季冈仁波齐</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 italic">Sacred Mountain Through the Seasons</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {seasons.map((season, index) => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark">{season.name}</h3>
              <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic">{season.nameEn}</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-kailash-gold font-medium text-sm mb-3">{season.months}</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">{season.description}</p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs italic mb-4">{season.descriptionEn}</p>
            <span class="inline-block bg-kailash-gold/10 text-kailash-dark text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">{season.highlight}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-kailash-gold">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">
        准备好亲身感受冈仁波齐的力量了吗？
      </h2>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
        Ready to Experience the Power of Kailash?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-kailash-dark/80 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="zh">
        了解历史是为了更好地理解当下。当您踏上转山之路时，您不仅是在行走，更是在延续三千年的信仰传承。
      </p>
      <p class="text-kailash-dark/80 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
        Understanding history helps us better understand the present. When you embark on the Kora, you are not just walking—you are continuing a 3000-year legacy of faith.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/guide" class="bg-kailash-dark text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-kailash-dark/90 transition" data-lang-content="zh">
          查看朝圣攻略
        </a>
        <a href="/guide" class="bg-kailash-dark text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-kailash-dark/90 transition" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
          View Pilgrimage Guide
        </a>
        <a href="/routes" class="bg-white text-kailash-dark px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition" data-lang-content="zh">
          了解转山路线
        </a>
        <a href="/routes" class="bg-white text-kailash-dark px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">
          Explore Kora Route
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
